FuncDef: The reset access-user dot1x-identity statistics command clears statistics about 802.1X Identity packets. The reset access-user dot1x-identity statistics command clears statistics about 802.1X Identity packets. This command is supported only on the CE6863H, CE6863H-K, CE6881H, CE6881H-K, CE6820H, CE6820H-K and CE6820S.
